{"id":3070,"date":"2018-02-19T20:19:35","date_gmt":"2018-02-20T04:19:35","slug":"silver-trucks","title":"Silver Trucks M Class &#038; L Class","content":"<p>In our recent Halloween box we included a set of trucks from <a href=\"http://www.silvertrucks.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Silver</a>, mixing it up with a selection of the Chad Ortiz M Class trucks and the Josh Kalis L Class trucks. In the KrakMag we laid out a little photo feature and gave you the low down on what makes each of these trucks so good!</p>\n<div id=\"attachment_3075\" style=\"width: 690px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-3075\" class=\"size-full wp-image-3075\" src=\"https://res.cloudinary.com/krak/image/upload/mag/uploads/silver-TimTim_frontbluntfakie_coultard.jpg\" alt=\"Chad Tim Tim, front blunt fakie. Photo: Jon Coultard\" width=\"680\" height=\"453\" srcset=\"https://res.cloudinary.com/krak/image/upload/mag/uploads/silver-TimTim_frontbluntfakie_coultard.jpg 680w, https://res.cloudinary.com/krak/image/upload/w_300/mag/uploads/silver-TimTim_frontbluntfakie_coultard.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 680px) 100vw, 680px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-3075\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Chad Tim Tim, front blunt fakie. Photo: Jon Coultard</p></div>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-3072\" src=\"https://res.cloudinary.com/krak/image/upload/mag/uploads/silver-mclass_main.jpg\" alt=\"Silver Trucks M Class\" width=\"680\" height=\"177\" srcset=\"https://res.cloudinary.com/krak/image/upload/mag/uploads/silver-mclass_main.jpg 680w, https://res.cloudinary.com/krak/image/upload/w_300/mag/uploads/silver-mclass_main.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 680px) 100vw, 680px\" /></p>\n<p>Silver M-Class trucks optimize turning ability with a refined structure and distinctive contours. A perfect amount of ground clearance, an exceptionally strong construction and dynamic components contribute to the overall quality, stability and smoothness of the M-Class. The performance level of the Silver <a href=\"http://www.silvertrucks.com/mclass.html\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">M-Class</a> easily meets and exceeds the high impact demands of a skateboard truck.</p>\n<div id=\"attachment_3074\" style=\"width: 690px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-3074\" class=\"size-full wp-image-3074\" src=\"https://res.cloudinary.com/krak/image/upload/mag/uploads/silver-SpencerBrown_nunez.jpg\" alt=\"Spencer Brown, nose grind. Photo: Nunez\" width=\"680\" height=\"497\" srcset=\"https://res.cloudinary.com/krak/image/upload/mag/uploads/silver-SpencerBrown_nunez.jpg 680w, https://res.cloudinary.com/krak/image/upload/w_300/mag/uploads/silver-SpencerBrown_nunez.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 680px) 100vw, 680px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-3074\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Spencer Brown, nose grind. Photo: Nunez</p></div>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-3071\" src=\"https://res.cloudinary.com/krak/image/upload/mag/uploads/silver-lclass_main.jpg\" alt=\"Silver Trucks L Class\" width=\"680\" height=\"177\" srcset=\"https://res.cloudinary.com/krak/image/upload/mag/uploads/silver-lclass_main.jpg 680w, https://res.cloudinary.com/krak/image/upload/w_300/mag/uploads/silver-lclass_main.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 680px) 100vw, 680px\" /></p>\n<p>Silver L-Class trucks feature a low profile structure designed for enhanced turning and ultimate control. In addition, the L-Class truck gives new meaning to the term light weight with its unique construction and quality components, including hollow kingpins, refined hangers and honed baseplates. Smooth performance, solid stability, and long lasting durability make <a href=\"http://www.silvertrucks.com/lclass.html\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">L-Class trucks</a> ideal for all levels of skateboarding.</p>\n<div id=\"attachment_3073\" style=\"width: 690px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-3073\" class=\"size-full wp-image-3073\" src=\"https://res.cloudinary.com/krak/image/upload/mag/uploads/silver-Mizurov_fsheel.jpg\" alt=\"Alex Mizurov, f/s heel. Photo courtesy of Silver\" width=\"680\" height=\"452\" srcset=\"https://res.cloudinary.com/krak/image/upload/mag/uploads/silver-Mizurov_fsheel.jpg 680w, https://res.cloudinary.com/krak/image/upload/w_300/mag/uploads/silver-Mizurov_fsheel.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 680px) 100vw, 680px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-3073\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Alex Mizurov, f/s heel. Photo courtesy of Silver</p></div>\n<h3><span style=\"color: #808080;\"><strong>This interview was originally featured in the printed KrakMag that shipped with the Halloween <a href=\"http://www.krakbox.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">KrakBox</a>. Want to get your hands on a copy of the next printed KrakMag? Want to receive epic skateboarding product every two months? Check out the <a href=\"http://www.krakbox.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">KrakBox</a> now!</strong></span></h3>\n","author":"kev","categories":["box"],"tags":["krakbox","krakmag","silver-trucks"],"featuredImages":[{"file":"silver-TimTim_Mclass_wiehl.jpg","width":680,"height":455,"mime_type":"image/jpeg","source_url":"https://res.cloudinary.com/krak/image/upload/mag/uploads/silver-TimTim_Mclass_wiehl.jpg"}],"video":""}